      "path": "audio/narrations/heat-equation/yunxi/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "方程的核心思想是：热量从高温区域流向低温区域。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "heat-equation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
